Subject: Re: [T2] HEATER FAN BLOWER

>just wondering if anyone can tell me where to wire up a fan heater blower.
>I tried to connect it to the coil but when i attach the wire the van dies
>out.

You can use the coil power to close a relay tying the blower to the battery 
(through a fuse). Your fan is drawing so many amps that the coil isn't 
getting any power.

Use that relay.

$6 at Radio Shack. $2 at Parts Express (web) but you pay shipping. Couple 
bucks for the fuse holder.


